# Mission Design Contract

- Every mission must map to a value/principle from the spec.
- Mission structure is mandatory: `goal -> interaction -> choice -> consequence -> progress update`.
- For MVP-1, prioritize mission "Responsibility" and make it fully playable end-to-end.
- Include at least one meaningful branch in player choice.
- Consequences must be visible to player (HUD/result screen/dialogue outcome).
- Keep mission text concise and clear; avoid vague outcomes.
- If adding mission content, update relevant docs/checklist status.
